About how many faculty when you left as department head?

00:18:37.507 --> 00:18:39.613
The head counted about 25.

00:18:39.633 --> 00:18:41.519
Okay.

00:18:41.539 --> 00:18:42.763
So it tripled?

00:18:46.394 --> 00:18:46.474
Yes.

